<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>CMASS-SALES 로그인</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3c72, #2a5298);
      color: #fff;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
      text-align: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }
    .btn {
      display: block;
      width: 80vw;
      max-width: 400px;
      margin: 1rem auto;
      padding: 2rem;
      font-size: 2rem;
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
      border: none;
      background: #fff;
      color: #1e3c72;
      font-weight: bold;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(30,60,114,0.2);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    }
    .btn:hover {
      background: #2a5298;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .admin-btn {
      background: #ff9800;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .admin-btn:hover {
      background: #fff;
      color: #ff9800;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>CMASS-SALES 영업일지 시스템</h1>
  <button class="btn" onclick="location.href='sales-input.html?user=송훈재'">송훈재 영업일지</button>
  <button class="btn" onclick="location.href='sales-input.html?user=임준호'">임준호 영업일지</button>
  <button class="btn" onclick="location.href='sales-input.html?user=조영환'">조영환 영업일지</button>
  <button class="btn admin-btn" onclick="location.href='dashboard.html'">관리자 대시보드</button>
  <h1>영업일지 목록</h1>
  <ul id="sales-list"></ul>
  <script>
      // Flask 백엔드 API에서 영업일지 목록 불러오기
      fetch('http://localhost:5000/sales')
          .then(response => response.json())
          .then(data => {
              const list = document.getElementById('sales-list');
              list.innerHTML = '';
              data.forEach(item => {
                  const li = document.createElement('li');
                  li.textContent = `교육청: ${item.office_of_education}, 지역: ${item.region}, 본사담당자: ${item.manager}, 학생 수: ${item.student_count}`;
                  list.appendChild(li);
              });
          });
  </script>
</body>
</html>